Cafe Ma Cherie: Ikemen Cafe

––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––

📱OTOME of Ikemen Cafe

Work at Ikemen Cafe! The protagonist who ended up working here after an encounter is actually... a girl?! 

––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––





Hi there! I'm Yuii 😘 I love playing games and watching anime. It's like a little time I have to escape from the reality. I LOVE IT! 💜
Do you know, by liking this video and subscribe to this channel, you really help me to put out more content and grow this channel. You are awesome! Thank you 💕
